Vendored schema files and their source versions:
  activity_view.rng  — Odoo 17.0 (stable across v15-v19)
  calendar_view.rng  — Odoo 17.0 (stable across v15-v19)
  common.rng         — Odoo 17.0 (compatible with v15-v19 view schemas)
  graph_view.rng     — Odoo 17.0 (stable across v15-v19)
  pivot_view.rng     — Odoo 17.0 (stable across v15-v19)
  search_view.rng    — Odoo 17.0 (stable across v15-v19)
  tree_view.rng      — Odoo 17.0 (used for v15-v17 <tree>-root list views)
  list_view.rng      — Odoo 18.0 (used for v18+ <list>-root list views)

NOTE — v18 tree→list rename: Odoo 18 renamed the list-view root tag from
<tree> to <list> and ships list_view.rng instead of tree_view.rng. Both
schemas are vendored here; the indexer selects version-aware:
  - v15-v17: view_type='tree' validated against tree_view.rng
  - v18+:    view_type='list' validated against list_view.rng
The shared common.rng (v17) is compatible with both schemas.

The indexer applies a VersionRegistry gate: only views from Odoo v15+ are
validated against these schemas to avoid false positives on older eras where
view grammar was different.

